{
  "stem": "11957.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- my father was working as a tailor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that they couldn't take away from him, because the [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] population around Dubno was mostly Ukrainians, and Polish, and Germans, and Russians.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when they wanted something, a new suit, a new coat, they had to come to my dad.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My dad should make it for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The advanced German-- German militaries that came into our town, they were all on motorcycles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We stood there and watched them, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] all on motorcycles.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't have any warning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all of a sudden, we start seeing those German soldiers on motorcycles, coming into town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not quite a deep blue, it's light blueish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was about 1 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I can't remember the day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I know we all ran out there to watch them come in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we had to live with it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they gave-- they gave orders to-- to where we lived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They only gave us about [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] four blocks to live in, between east and west, and seven blocks between north and south.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That area was for-- a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to build a 10-foot-- 10 feet fence around that area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we couldn't get out from there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had to go through guards to come in and go out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They posted guards around there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, my aunt and her family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, very bad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] When you went out-- out from the ghetto on the street, you had to be careful not to walk on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because if you walked on the sidewalk, they'd just throw you off the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
